                <head ana="#head_untitled-inferred-from-preceding-sibling-head">[Untitled]</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Port au Prince</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1915-05-06">
                            <hi rend="italic">May 6, 1915</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Bobo with a large cavalry escort entered Cape Haitien yesterday at 1 o’clock.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Davis</hi>.</signed>
                </closer>
